{"tid":2268491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈，拜登贏出了美國總統大選的民意調查，僅此而已！","createTime":"2020-11-03T00:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T18:12:48.000Z","uid":43785,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"09dcf57a31aa25f8768cbb632446921d152febc6","tid":2268491,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T00:33:48.000Z","msg":"我宣佈，拜登贏出了美國總統大選的民意調查，僅此而已！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GB52bKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGB52bKj.jpg&h=98698b24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統大選進入倒數，Trump一日之內連踩五場，橫跨五個州拉票，佛羅里達州果場仲要係凌晨一點。<br />\n<br />\n雖然民調指Trump係賓州落後，但其造勢大會人潮一望無際，連民主黨賓州副州長John Fetterma也驚嘆話「我唔理民調點樣講... 總統在賓州好受歡迎，PS唔倒，快啲出嚟投票。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMhTirn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMhTirn.jpg&h=58eb4ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQJCK6H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQJCK6H.jpg&h=a235b437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHRpp63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHRpp63.jpg&h=573e6efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PbPZd0p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPbPZd0p.jpg&h=e01d3ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4V5T0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4V5T0q.jpg&h=59b5cd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/11/03/083236_c1de39fa790b0de7854485156d2526cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F11%2F03%2F083236_c1de39fa790b0de7854485156d2526cf.jpg&h=d3ff1eeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0aeb6bf7f304aa132e58ab8c5c3fc6b2ccedaf65","tid":2268491,"uid":229954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11